'''利福勒縣'''（{{lang-en|Le Flore County}}）是[[美國|美國]][[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]]東南部的一個縣，東鄰[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]，面積4,165平方公里。根据[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]，本縣共有人口48,109人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/ |title=2010 census data |accessdate=2013-10-05 |archive-date=2011-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706203009/http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://censusviewer.com/county/OK/Le%20Flore |title=CensusViewer: Population of Le Flore County, Oklahoma |accessdate=2013-10-05 |archive-date=2019-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531234802/http://censusviewer.com/county/OK/Le%20Flore |dead-url=no }}</ref>本縣縣治為[[波托_(奧克拉荷馬州)|波托]]（{{lang|en|Poteau}}）。{{GR|6}}本縣是[[史密斯堡_(阿肯色州)|史密斯堡]][[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]-奧克拉荷馬州[[史密斯堡大都會統計區|大都會統計區]]的一部份。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2007/CBSA-EST2007-01.csv | title = Annual Estimates of the Population of Metropolitan and Micropolitan Statistical Areas: April 1, 2000 to July 1, 2007 (CBSA-EST2007-01) | format = [[comma-separated_values|CSV]] | work = 2007 Population Estimates | publisher = [[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]], Population Division | date = 2008-03-27 | accessdate = 2008-03-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080912170654/http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2007/CBSA-EST2007-01.csv | archive-date = 2008-09-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="EOHC-LeFloreCo">O"Dell, Larry. ''Encyclopedia of Oklahoma History and Culture''. "LeFlore County." {{cite web |url=http://digital.library.okstate.edu/encyclopedia/entries/L/LE007.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-10-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104005608/http://digital.library.okstate.edu/encyclopedia/entries/L/LE007.html |archivedate=2012-11-04 }}</ref>

==歷史==
[[File:George_Mayo_Map.png|thumb]]
俄克拉何馬州喬克托國於1820年與美國簽定多克的斯坦條約，割讓包含本縣在內的土地以換取另一片土地。於1830年，他們又簽定舞蹈兔河條約，將更多土地割予美國，並迫使割讓地的原住民遷離。<ref name="EOHC-LeFloreCo"/>

本縣於1907年7月16日成立。縣名紀念[[喬克托族|喬克托族]]酋長[[格林伍德·利福勒|格林伍德·利福勒]]。<ref>Kane, J. N. and C. C. Aiken. The American Counties: Origins of County Names Dates of Creation and Population Data 1950-2000. Lanham, MD.: Scarecrow Press, 2005.</ref>

